{"tid":674896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無線報薩「塞」(coi3)克斯公爵同夫人哈里、梅根婚後首次出席公開活動","createTime":"2018-05-23T05:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T03:19:03.000Z","uid":158270,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"80f06ff7d94c00c6094b666ec52cc0dbb78c0ed8","tid":674896,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"無線報馬丁路德金遇「刺」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/621456/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/621456/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n繼上次發現不明讀音，今次我聽到無線主播將Sussex嘅中譯薩塞克斯個塞讀成要塞個塞coi3。但我認為塞喺依度應該讀sak1，即係塞車、木塞個塞。<br />\n我估：<br />\nSussex<br />\nSu--薩<br />\nSe--塞<br />\nX--克斯<br />\n考慮塞嘅兩個讀音（coi3, sak1）應讀s字頭嗰個先接近sussex。<br />\n至於點解會讀錯，可能係因為內地嘅塞字得一個音，堵塞同要塞兩個塞同音，令主播出錯。"},{"pid":"2b2ba7c1108583afe94f5dfa5d3d0430ca976f5f","tid":674896,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf37271e2de20d4d221a0f6bfc86f06d1fb5df53","tid":674896,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"好多人見呢個字都係會偏向讀「賽」，除非係詞語連埋，不過CCTVB班報新聞嘅垃圾水平係咁上下，之前成撚日報到窒吓窒吓，而家多多單唔查字典 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6c4b125c1e34f64ef65ed5f7857f87b93961f4","tid":674896,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"刺有乜問題"},{"pid":"856554b61f522b76b9ff030acf6b0deaf9dec4fa","tid":674896,"uid":19501,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"薩塞克斯，又係嗰啲支那譯音?<br />\n上wiki，見到粵語係譯修適士<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/修適士大學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%BF%AE%E9%81%A9%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8&d=S1Ywlxr8tDy42Wc%2BRmdR